                    <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="cross"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg> <span data-i18n="comp.old.5">Scheduling? Cron + eigene Logik</span></li>
