                    <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="check"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> <span data-i18n="comp.new.4">Live-Dashboard mit Echtzeit-Events</span></li>
                    <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="check"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> <span data-i18n="comp.new.5">Eingebautes Scheduling mit Cron</span></li>
